ded:</strong>                    <br>     <ul class="bb_ul"><li><strong>OS:</strong> WindowsÂź XP (with SP2) or Windows VistaÂź (with SP1)                    <br>     </li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> IntelÂź CoreÂź 2 Duo E6600 2.4GHz','','');
